   Univ Michigan, Dept Ecol \& Evolut Biol, Ann Arbor, MI 48109 USA.
   Univ Utrecht, Dept Philosophy, Natl Herbanium Nederland, NL-3584 CS Utrecht, Netherlands.
   Univ San Francisco Quito, Tiputini Biodivers Stn, Quito, Ecuador.},
DOI = {10.2307/25065746},
