   Suetsugu, Kenji, Kobe Univ, Grad Sch Sci, Dept Biol, Kobe, Hyogo 6578501, Japan.
   Suetsugu, Kenji, Kobe Univ, Inst Adv Res, Kobe, Hyogo, Japan.},
